0.title: UI/UX Designer needed with Figma, Sketch & Adobe Creative Suite expertise
0.description:
We are seeking a talented UI/UX Designer to join our team for an exciting design project. 

**Required Skills & Expertise:**
• Expert proficiency in Figma, Sketch, and Adobe Creative Suite
• Strong experience in Wireframing and creating detailed user flows
• Advanced Prototyping skills to bring designs to life
• Expertise in Responsive Design for multi-device experiences
• Intermediate level experience with substantial portfolio demonstrating these skills

**Project Details:**
• Medium-sized project scope (well-defined requirements)
• Timeline: 1-3 months duration
• Hourly rate: $30-60/hr based on experience
• Looking for someone with substantial experience in UI/UX design

**What You'll Do:**
• Create wireframes and user flows for new features
• Design high-fidelity mockups and interactive prototypes
• Ensure responsive design across all devices and platforms
• Collaborate with our team to refine and iterate on designs
• Deliver clean, organized design files using Figma/Sketch

**What We're Looking For:**
• Portfolio showcasing expertise in the required tools and skills
• Strong communication skills and ability to work collaboratively
• Attention to detail and commitment to delivering high-quality work
• Experience with modern design principles and user-centered design

This is an excellent opportunity to work on impactful design projects. Please share your portfolio demonstrating your expertise in the mentioned tools and skills.
